{"tid":2153514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好比廠商會班契弟賣小強, 有確鑿證據呢班人係警暴的主犯","createTime":"2020-08-12T14:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T11:11:40.000Z","uid":26770,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2f50cae09efb9ddedbd613b56779015946747ceb","tid":2153514,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200213/2IMRURN2HQ3TQ2L7VQUWUJ4JGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2F2IMRURN2HQ3TQ2L7VQUWUJ4JGQ%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7QESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=de3bc60a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2F2IMRURN2HQ3TQ2L7VQUWUJ4JGQ%2F&h=c67d7e92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200213/2IMRURN2HQ3TQ2L7VQUWUJ4JGQ/</a><br />\n廠商會大量支持警暴的言論大家應該一早知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廠商會行政總裁楊立門促追究罷工醫護,表面上係迫害參與罷工的醫護<br />\n<strong>實際係報復醫護人員踢爆警魔性侵/私刑示威者</strong><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">楊垃門身居行政總裁係代表廠商會的意志</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>班pr已經收order講香港廠家只係做生意, 遭美中大戰波及好慘<br />\n就係想用香港民間聲音去夾美國政府</strong>"},{"pid":"531e1439c5908bf35aa025a0230f9440df1c3467","tid":2153514,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"楊立門仆街冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8ac4d9bfef155f748d653ee308e5fd49e3a6e5","tid":2153514,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:46:58.000Z","msg":"當日聲勢最高時大把行頭都有工業行動<br />\n清洗教育界係因為呢個係中共最高指示,意識形態問題<br />\n<ins>郁醫護有咩原因?仲要係瘟疫盛行時郁手?</ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong>睇下美國議員同un人權委員會重點關注香港警魔性暴行大家就明</strong><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">廠商會班契弟就等同企係香港人同人類文明的對立面</span>"},{"pid":"972d3621bcba96af46358931564eb58181fe714f","tid":2153514,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislik